{"tid":549043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚴寒返工返學】料市區連續兩日7°C 北區或3°C","createTime":"2018-02-03T08:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T10:53:58.000Z","uid":47272,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"23dd31c98595224857b5e04b2213475f90613a5c","tid":549043,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T08:24:24.000Z","msg":"冬季季候風補充來襲，天文台預計華南未來數天早晚持續寒冷，市區周日一（4、5日）早上均低見7&deg;C，跌至嚴寒水平，其中周日的預測較之前再調低1度。至於其電腦直接輸出、未經人手修正的分區氣溫預報顯示，屆時新界將再低兩三度，其中北區的打鼓嶺或連續兩日只有3&deg;C。<br />\n寒潮過後，天文台展望下周中期本港日間氣溫會逐漸回升，日夜溫差較大。而一股偏東氣流會在下周後期影響廣東沿岸，該區漸轉多雲。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180203&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57784279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180203%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57784279&d=v6tcZVhR5zdeH8CLGWrrsZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=aecc385c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180203%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57784279&h=1c9acca2\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180203&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57784279</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zv7bosth\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzv7bosth&h=c92a2d03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f058c1bd47ca42440292853124a64bbf7ea968c5","tid":549043,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"995fab3dc5e4cc4f451581066bf42746a8a8e67a","tid":549043,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"極端天氣好恐怖"},{"pid":"5753c2a5548e892d07a6353c366ee2f8254cefc7","tid":549043,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:19:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e44e29508410ddf9a6bce80c384d6c2ec1c11702","tid":549043,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:31:33.000Z","msg":"大交合又要冚家剷"},{"pid":"e34b77b0bbf7